{"tid":1158581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)老母報左瑜珈班","createTime":"2019-05-17T05:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T12:59:07.000Z","uid":173160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bcedbb38a119d0e16a79d9d057f26e225d4215db","tid":1158581,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"今朝我老母whatsapp同我講報左1年瑜珈班<br />\n我問佢報左幾錢,佢話1萬蚊任上,我心知不妙叫佢影張合約比我<br />\n佢一開頭無應我,後尾先話原來係3萬幾蚊2年半約,怕我鬧佢<br />\n間野叫 elimentfitlax  ,係我老母早兩日行路比佢地氹下講下比左錢<br />\n佢第日自己都覺得唔對路想退錢但無辦法退  佢自己都話唔係成日有時間上堂<br />\n(我老母係D比較蠢既人.買野好多時無咩點諗 唔識拒絕人,之前已經試過買過好多幾千蚊件又唔著既衫褲鞋物,一堆唔知有無用既保險  等等)<br />\n而家應該點做?"},{"pid":"43fff140e0a531643ff0aac91194fa398598640a","tid":1158581,"uid":29315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"好似有冷靜期?"},{"pid":"aee7451d9731c7fd9032b7d8b9e50c87d9828a85","tid":1158581,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"咁睇清楚合約條款 睇下有無得救囉<br />\n然後收撚埋晒你老母啲錢呀卡呀咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0825667b1b9432d9babdebdbfdeb4c27e792ffd2","tid":1158581,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"而家等老母翻屋企先可以影個合約比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5a4129b9e580818f6612203a6c0027726d64a0","tid":1158581,"uid":173160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ce8a1f994ca01a912507a0f0e1e5c20ac1339a7","tid":1158581,"uid":19124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"睇下有無冷靜期<br />\n<br />\n不過得我都報左呢間 佢有唔同course上 有spin boxing 唔同既瑜珈 不過勁耐無去過上了"},{"pid":"e3d5d605ebc698f84042a0dae1663fa0ebef9f04","tid":1158581,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"如果無冷靜期有無方法退到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi